net.proteusframework.core.usertype

Class LongAnyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.type.AbstractType
      • org.hibernate.type.AnyType
        • net.proteusframework.core.usertype.LongAnyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AssociationType, CompositeType, Type

    public class LongAnyType
extends AnyType
    AnyType implementation that is used when the Entity Identifiers of the objects will be Longs.

    For an alternative. See http://www.hibernate.org/hib_docs/annotations/reference/en/html_single/#entity-hibspec-singleassoc-any

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
